                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "Developed and integrated an Automated Material Handling Technology (AMHT) kit for the Army?s ATLAS II 10,000 pound capability forklift. This  includes the hardware and software necessary for the vehicle to conduct its missions both autonomously and semi-autonomously, and to demonstrate the AMHT kit through a series of tests and obstacle courses that were developed from the vehicle?s performance specification and were designed to imitate its mission profile."
